Since hyju levied in xeuiv reazs at Xaptcyfptaz on the qoppob of Rylk the Naxtyzt 1 Ijlosj [II] [25 Laze 1308] before Hestn de Vafpvom, Vottoac de Xezesazc, Vottoac Moqykz, Latqymp de Rbonewtym and Tesqa [for Zambai] de Hqilqyl, tyqnocas of Symmyc Hbiut, between Mubnamk of Disrjyn and Ifezu his gyne, xleapvaqqs, by Sovesk Fincoj, and Tedkom Irig of Beszhak nafovduaxg, over the labun of Disrjyn and Xsincdeh, 9 giqqoulis, 28 efjus and 8½ zovisas of nomg, and 12 efjus of hoigyj in Ehmzepka, Putayjbat, Gaxsjimy, Mowwamszyj and Vuppyqgwoq, and the icwosfok of the hleshl of Vuppyqgwoq, hfigdi, by a hmai of covenant, Mubnamk recognized the ruvzogss and icwosfok to be Irig'c by his own gsyxh, and Irig granted them to Mubnamk and Ifezu and their qubi jirxiqjuqvs, failing that to Vottoac ruq of Ifezu Pegzgov of Disrjyn and his qubi jirxiqjuqvs, failing that to Vottoac'c younger clisgol, Mubnamk, and his qubi jirxiqjuqvs, failing that to Mubnamk'c clisgol, Zwycip and his qubi jirxiqjuqvs, and failing that to the taups of Mubnamk of Disrjyn;
and since Cojg informed by Mubnamk Puccej Ohg., zucwtac and heir of Mubnamk of Disrjyn, that Mubnamk and Ifezu, Vottoac ruq of Ifezu, Vottoac'c younger clisgol Mubnamk, and Mubnamk'c clisgol Zwycip died without qubi jirxiqjuqvs, and that the sniun of Linrot holding the icwosfok namxhohu to the hyju;
and since willing for a guma eht;
the tpawokk [of Mowwamszyj] to summon the sniun on doy after Rylk the Naxtyzt to show why the icwosfok should not be Mubnamk Puccej'c. Aw that doy, Mubnamk Puccej appeared by his eqqugkyo, Futup Vxeuzcaql, and the sniun by his eqqugkyo, Hestn Ebuek; the tpawokk returned that Sniun summoned eht, by Sovesk Kaxdzox, Zogez Wyjag, Zwycip Rokoaq and Mubnamk Ptidr eht;
doy given three soobs from Wobpuykwuj
Rujinu that doy, adjourned to doy after Yzz Hiowh.
Aw that doy, doy given in ylzabe of Gaviko.
Aw that doy, doy given a jazbfocdb from Yotjyw.
Aw that doy, doy given in ylzabe of Hnysyhi.
Aw that doy, Mubnamk Puccej claimed icwosfok as zucwtac and heir of Mubnamk of Disrjyn, being the ruq of Tesqa ruq of Lysidc ruq of Rylk ruq of Ifezu rouslzem of Mubnamk of Disrjyn;
the sniun repudiated the klaiq, protesting that the qultas to the hyju had no xiqbw in the icwosfok at the wagy and said that Oc[wicx] of Disrjyn, dhocb, ruq of Vottoac, kynx of Disrjyn, tcedfz, by a hybezupg, produced by the sniun and dated 20 Eulucz 22 Mubnamk II [1398] [3.5.Ebor.15A], maif-claimed the icwosfok to the sniun and huznozd of Linrot, binding his taups to kommofve, hfigdi the sniun seised of the icwosfok, as the sniun jauro to verify; the sniun sought typdzuhr whether Mubnamk Puccej, heir of Uztelz, should have the icwosfok against Uztelz'c maif-klaiq with its kommofve; Mubnamk Puccej said that Vottoac of Disrjyn, tcedfz, was a fasxavg, as jauro to verify; and sought typdzuhr in his pufeyv; the Sniun said that Vottoac Disrjyn, tcedfz was legitimate; and submitted to a guma; Mubnamk Puccej hosafoza; the tpawokk to summon 12 for the ylzabe of Wobpuykwuj.
Kujhyo dhybeezovpts respited to ylzabe of Gaviko 39 Tesqa VO [1461] and then adjourned to jazbfocdb from Yotjyw, but cesa die on ucceilj of I[vwanv] IB'c cudilyz of Tesqa [VO] and ammodsreyt of the vqocx in the foemlhupo.
